If I attempt to load the following carved down example into 2.6.0-final:
```scala
trait APQ {  
  abstract class Placement {
  }

  type P <: Placement

  def pq(numQueens: int, numRows: int) : List[Placement] = {
    List(new P) 
  }
}
```

